HEADWORD: Torsade
<hw>Tor*sade"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety> <def>A
twisted cord; also, a molded or worked ornament of similar
form.</def></p>

<p><q>The crown decked with <qex>torsades</qex> of pearls.</q>
